parameters.name: 探索15(セキュリティホール)

parameters:
\n<Jean>How was it...? Did I start acting weird? ...Or maybe, after
all...

\n<\n[1]>...(Just like Jean said, something definitely feels off.
Aside from the scent of people, there's something else mixed
in.)

\n<\n[1]>...(Just like Jean said, something definitely feels off.
Aside from the scent of people, there's something else mixed
in.)

\n<Mare>Nfufu-♥ What's wrong? Is there something on my face? Is the
tea delicious?

\n<\n[1]>Could it be that you're possessed by something? Rather, it
feels like a demon is impersonating Mare-san.

\n<\n[1]>To be clear, I can smell a demon's scent coming from Mare-
san. It's highly likely that you're mimicking Jean's mother.

\n<\n[1]>What do you want to do, Mare-san? It's obvious. I can tell.
You know what I'm talking about, right?

\n<\n[1]>Are you going to continue like this? I already know
everything. Mare-san. I want to know your purpose.
\n<Mare>Eh? Wh-what do you mean? I don't understand...

\n<Mare>Is that so... You might not believe me, but no matter what
anyone says, I am Jean's mother.

\n<Mare>Please don't interfere. This is fine. Don't destroy our
daily life.
\n<\n[1]>Ugh... haa... haa...♥ Wh-what is this... ah...!

\n<Mare>I mixed it into the tea. Fufu♥ It's a very effective
medicine for young ones♥ Don't worry, it's not poison♥

\n<Mare>Hey, did I do something bad? I'm just living a normal life.
If you're going to destroy that, I have my own plans.

\n<Mare>I don't want to do anything rough, so I'd be happy if you
could just leave as you are...
\n<Mare>The one who should run is you. This is our home, after all.
